import React, { Component } from 'react';
import { connect } from 'react-redux'

import { Form, Button } from 'semantic-ui-react'

class SessionForm extends Component {
  constructor() {
    super()
    this.state = {
      date:'',
      location: '',
      hours: 0,
      buyin: 0,
      cashout: 0,
      amount: 0.00
    }
  }

  render() {
    return (
      <Form>
        <Form.Group>
          <Form.Field width={5}>
            <label>Date</label>
            <input
              name='date'
              type='date'
              placeholder='Date...'
            />
          </Form.Field>
          <Form.Field width={11}>
            <label>Location</label>
            <input
              name='location'
              placeholder='Location...'
            />
          </Form.Field>
        </Form.Group>
        <Form.Group widths='equal'>
          <Form.Field>
            <label>Hours</label>
            <input
              name='hours'
              type='number'
              step='.5'
              placeholder='Hours Played...'
            />
          </Form.Field>
          <Form.Field>
            <label>Bought In</label>
            <input
              name='buyin'
              type='number'
              placeholder='$'
            />
          </Form.Field>
          <Form.Field>
            <label>Cashed Out</label>
            <input
              name='cashout'
              type='number'
              placeholder='$'
            />
          </Form.Field>
        </Form.Group>
        <Button type='submit'>Submit</Button>
      </Form>
    )
  }

}

const mapDispatchToProps = dispatch => {
  return {

  }
}

export default connect(null, mapDispatchToProps)(SessionForm);
